ZH: 他们的行为完全背道而驰，违背了公司的价值观。
EN: Their actions are completely contrary to the values of the company.

ZH: 他的说辞和他的行为背道而驰。
EN: His words and actions are in direct contradiction.

ZH: 这个政策背道而驰于我们的发展需要。
EN: This policy goes against our developmental needs.

ZH: 公司的决策背道而驰于员工的利益。
EN: The company's decision is contrary to the interests of the employees.

ZH: 这项提议背道而驰于我们的原则。
EN: This proposal is contrary to our principles.

ZH: 她的行为背道而驰于社会的道德规范。
EN: Her behavior is contrary to societal moral norms.

ZH: 这样做会背道而驰于规章制度。
EN: Doing so would be in violation of regulations.

ZH: 我的观点与他们背道而驰。
EN: My perspective contradicts theirs.

ZH: 学生们的行为和老师的期望背道而驰。
EN: The students' behavior is contrary to the teacher's expectations.

ZH: 这种行为明显背道而驰于我们的信条。
EN: This behavior clearly goes against our creed.

ZH: 如果你这样做，你会背道而驰于你的承诺。
EN: If you do this, you would be going back on your promise.

ZH: 这种言论背道而驰于我们社会的价值观。
EN: This kind of speech is contrary to the values of our society.

ZH: 他的决定背道而驰于我们的合作计划。
EN: His decision contradicts our collaboration plan.

ZH: 这个项目的实施背道而驰于我们的原始计划。
EN: The implementation of this project deviates from our original plan.

ZH: 这个政策的效果完全背道而驰。
EN: The outcome of this policy is completely contrary.

ZH: 这项决定与企业的长远利益背道而驰。
EN: This decision is contrary to the long-term interests of the company.

ZH: 这个行动背道而驰于法律法规。
EN: This action is in violation of the law.

ZH: 学生们对老师的指示背道而驰。
EN: The students disobeyed the teacher's instructions.

ZH: 我们应该遵循原则，而不是背道而驰。
EN: We should follow principles instead of going against them.

ZH: 这个项目的目标背道而驰于我们的价值观。
EN: The objectives of this project go against our values.
